9. kommunala
10. riksdagen

There are 12 words in 2 cases ('uranbrytning' and 'urantillgångarna' are composed of 'uran' and other words), and 'Bl.a.' is not taken into account since it is abbreviated from its actual long word. It is very common in Swedish, so it probably is counted as a normal word and left out here but note that it actually is of three different letters but still counts as one word, it means "(bland annat), because of 'a', 'a' = one because of many other abbreviations contain even more instances of 'a' and many other letters. ('alltså', eg in Swedish)
